EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1000Z TO 1900Z DAILY
   10 THRU 12 FEB WITHIN 45 MILES
   OF 57-24.4N 008-53.0W. VESSELS INTENDING
   TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16
   OR PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 122000Z FEB 17.
